1630
1930
GOODRICH MASSACRE
TEN RODS EAST STOOD THE
HOUSE OF BENJAMIN GOODRICH
WHO, WITH HIS WIFE AND TWO
CHILDREN, WAS SLAIN BY THE
INDIANS ON OCTOBER 23, 1692.
MASSACHUSETTS BAY COLONY
TERCENTENARY COMMISSION
